PrecisOrder giving notice of the National Guideline for ENGINE COOLANT CONCENTRATE (ECP-43-91) specifying a minimum recycled content of 20% base fluid prior to January 1, 1995, increasing to 40% on or after that date, requiring recycled content in packaging materials, and stipulating that certified products meet the requirements of industry performance standards equal to those set for engine coolant concentrates made from virgin ethylene or propylene glycol.
Attachments
